channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: WILLIAMS: Los Angeles' Insane Clown Posse
Southern border migrant encounters decrease slightly but gotaways still surge under Biden
item.description: The number of migrants encounters at the southern border declined slightly in April but gotaways in the past three years were more than the entire decade spanning 2010-2020.

item.title: Sen. Paul to Newsmax: Scientist Affirms Gain-of-Function in Wuhan
item.description: In a Wednesday interview on Newsmax, Sen. Rand Paul, R-Ky., accused Dr. Anthony Fauci of evading responsibility for funding gain-of-function research at the Wuhan Institute of Virology, citing revelations from a prominent scientist and ongoing investigations. Paul spoke out,...

item.title: Pro-Hamas Protesters Take Over UC Irvine Building, Quickly Find Out Things Are Different in Orange County
GOP turns up heat on House Dems with high-pressure Israel vote Thursday
item.description: The House is set to vote on a bill to block the Biden administration from halting offensive aid shipments to Israel.

item.title: Stephen Miller to Newsmax: Biden Campaign Miscalculated on Debates
item.description: President Joe Biden's reelection campaign miscalculated by challenging Donald Trump to two debates, believing the former president would not accept on their terms, Stephen Miller, a former senior adviser in the Trump administration, told Newsmax on Wednesday.

item.title: Biden Gives Snippy Response to Question About Debate, Staff Shoves Media Out, Debate Moderators Announced
'Must apologize': Vulnerable House Dem faces renewed backlash over comparison involving 9/11 terrorist
item.description: Congresswoman Marcy Kaptur is drawing renewed criticism over a comment where she compared the American Revolution to religious turmoil in the Middle East and Usama bin Laden.

item.title: Lara Trump to Newsmax: Trump Called Biden's Bluff on Debates
item.description: Lara Trump told Newsmax on Wednesday that former President Donald Trump called Joe Biden's bluff by immediately accepting the debate terms offered by the president's camp.

item.title: Raging Bull Attacks Woman on Mexican Beach
Michael Cohen returns as final witness in NYC AG Bragg's criminal prosecution of Trump
item.description: Defense attorneys for former President Trump are expected to continue their cross-examination of Michael Cohen when court resumes Thursday morning

item.title: DeSantis Signs Florida Bill Making Climate Change a Lesser Priority
item.description: Climate change will be a lesser priority in Florida and largely disappear from state statutes under legislation signed Wednesday by Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis that also bans power-generating wind turbines offshore or near the state's lengthy coastline.

item.title: Report: Soros Pumps $81M to Censor Election Speech Online
item.description: A media group funded by billionaire leftist George Soros is seeking to implement a global plan to pressure Big Tech social media platforms to censor more content before November's presidential election.
